column99: Kok / cook / cuoco - Italian restaurant in Denmark
column100:
ENGLISH: 
 Italian restaurant  "Enzo & C - uncompromized italian kitchen"  is searching for a cook with experience in the italian kitchen. 
 You will be part of a big team of Italien colleagues. 
 - Sallery after experience 
 - Possibility for room  
 - 5 working days per week  
 The restaurant is situated in Vejle, Denmark. 
 See www.enzo-c.dk 
 Please send CV to enzo@enzo-c.dk 
 ITALIANO: 
 Ristorante italiano  "Enzo & C - uncompromized italian kitchen"  cerca cuoco/chef. 
 Farai parte di un team di colleghi italiani. 
 - Stipendio secondo esperienze 
 - Possibilitá di alloggio 
 - 5 giorni lavorativi settimanali 
 Il ristorante e situato nella cittá di Vejle in Danimarca 
 Il sito, www.enzo-c.dk 
 Manda il  CV alla mail enzo@enzo-c.dk
